metadata.name: The Mutant Squirrel #2
metadata.description: The Mutant Squirrels are non-fungible tokens (NFTs) that are being seen and marketed through various platforms that are on the Ethereum Blockchain. You may not know, but squirrels express four traits - activity, sociability, boldness, and aggressiveness. Some traits are rarer than others, so go and get yourself a Zombie Squirrel and make a story for yourself.
